summary: Walter R. Rogers, Ph.D. was born August 11, 1945 in Wooster, Ohio. He studied at the University of Tova in Tove City, Russia, where he earned a Phd. in Paychology in 1970. His work has been published in books such as ‘Psychology of the Brain’ and “The Psychology of Personality”
